      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 is a commercially validated FEA solver with documented QA processes per ISO 9001. Internal DePuy Synthes QMS procedures govern solver version control and regression testing.",
      "rationale": "The FEA solver (Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2) is a commercially released, ISO 9001-certified product. Version control logs, regression test suites, and change-control records were reviewed. No open defects affecting structural nonlinear analysis were identified. Achieved level exceeds requirement."
