      "rationale": "The validation activity directly tests the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct under the ASTM F1717 protocol, which is the same device and test method as the COU. The FEA model geometry, material assignments, and boundary conditions are identical between the validation and COU predictions. No extrapolation beyond the validated domain is required for the regulatory submission."
